if you are required to report for active military duty in any branch of the united states armed forces, you are entitled to receive up to 30 calendar days of paid military leave for emergency, temporary and/or indefinite assignments in a fiscal year upon meeting eligibility criteria, if required. see the military leave information sheet [pdf] for information about eligibility, employee responsibilities and benefits. complete the leave request of absence form [pdf] and submit it to the leave program manager. for additional information contact up-leaves@sjsu.edu .  university-personnel@sjsu.edu up north: 408-924-2450 up south: 408-924-2250  up webmaster up north administration building 242 up south upd building 3rd floor 